If you use PyProSAIL in your academic work then please cite it as follows:

Wilson, R. T., PyProSAIL, Available from https://github.com/robintw/PyProSAIL

In BibTeX format:

@electronic{,
  author = {Wilson, R. T.},
  year = {2013},
  title = {PyProSAIL},
  url = {https://github.com/robintw/PyProSAIL}
}
